245
00:13:25,205 --> 00:13:26,672
I'm not so sure

246
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,241
it's the long
hours hurting you.

247
00:13:29,309 --> 00:13:31,243
Yeah.

248
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:34,747
Well, I see Gulley
every day.

249
00:13:34,814 --> 00:13:36,782
He looks good.

250
00:13:36,850 --> 00:13:39,418
I saw him
this morning.

251
00:13:39,486 --> 00:13:42,354
His arm's broken.

252
00:13:42,422 --> 00:13:43,989
I saw that.

253
00:13:44,057 --> 00:13:45,157
It's okay.

254
00:13:45,225 --> 00:13:47,192
Yeah. He's
doing great.

255
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,461
He's a good kid.

256
00:13:51,331 --> 00:13:52,698
(Kailey exhales)

257
00:13:52,766 --> 00:13:54,066
Is there a game around?

258
00:13:54,134 --> 00:13:55,668
You see anything?

259
00:13:55,735 --> 00:13:59,371
Even if there
were, I mean...

260
00:13:59,439 --> 00:14:01,306
you're a mess.

261
00:14:01,374 --> 00:14:03,108
You got enough
for hotel room?

262
00:14:03,176 --> 00:14:07,046
Yeah, but, uh, I'd rather
use it to get a game.

263
00:14:07,113 --> 00:14:08,347
Want to sleep here a bit?

264
00:14:08,415 --> 00:14:09,715
You mind?

265
00:14:09,783 --> 00:14:11,216
Go ahead.

266
00:14:11,284 --> 00:14:13,052
Thanks.

267
00:14:13,119 --> 00:14:14,553
(sniffles)

268
00:14:14,621 --> 00:14:17,456
Come get me if there's something
I should be awake for, okay?

269
00:14:17,524 --> 00:14:19,525
Got you.

